title: PC Gamer Magazine USA January 2013
description: PC Gamer brings you in-depth previews, exclusive feature stories, and the most hard-hitting reviews every month in the world's best-selling PC games magazine! Every month you'll get the inside scoop on the most exciting games in every genre from first-person shooters to MMORPGs and cutting-edge games from independent developers, along with detailed strategy guides, how-tos, and the latest news on mods and PC gaming hardware from the best-known authorities in PC gaming. PC Gamer helps you get the most out of the most powerful gaming platform in the world.
